This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image segmentation tasks. It may also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories as it proposes a novel activation function and loss function for the neural network. Additionally, it may belong to the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-category as it uses a deep neural network architecture. Finally, it may belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category as it deals with biomedical images.
